#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Kronometer"
msgstr "Kronometer"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Chronometer"
msgstr "Chronometro"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"Kronometer is a stopwatch application. It features the basic stopwatch "
"actions (pause/resume/reset/laps), as well as the ability to save the times "
"and resume them later. Kronometer is part of the KDE Extragear collection, "
"within the Utils sub-module."
msgstr ""
"Kronometer es un applicatin de chronometro. Illo presenta le actiones basic "
"de chronometro (pausa/resume/reduce a zero/gyros), tal como le habilitate de "
"salveguardar los plus tarde. Kronometer es parte del collection KDE "
"Extragear, intra le sub-modulo de Utils."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:17
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Characteristicas:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:19
msgid "Start/pause/resume the stopwatch widget"
msgstr "Strta/Pausa/Reprende le widget de stopparhorologio"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:20
msgid "Laps recording: you can capture the stopwatch time when you want"
msgstr ""
"Registration de gyros: tu pote capturar le tempore de chronometro quando tu "
"vole"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:21
msgid ""
"Lap times sorting: you can easily find the shortest lap time or the longest "
"one"
msgstr ""
"Ordinar tempores de gyro: tu pote facilemente trovar le plus breve o le plus "
"longe tempore de gyro"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:22
msgid "Reset the stopwatch widget and the lap times"
msgstr "Reprende (reuce a zero) le widhet de chronometro e le tempores de gyro"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:23
msgid "Time format settings: you can choose the stopwatch granularity"
msgstr ""
"Preferentias de formato de tempore: tu pote seliger le granularitate del "
"chronometro"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:24
msgid ""
"Times saving and resuming: you can save the stopwatch status and resume it "
"later"
msgstr ""
"Salveguardar e reprender tempores: tu pote salveguardar le stato de "
"chronometro e reprender loo plus tarde"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:25
msgid ""
"Font customization: you can choose the fonts for each of the stopwatch digits"
msgstr ""
"Personalisation de Font: tu pote seliger le font per cata cifras del "
"chronometro"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:26
msgid ""
"Color customization: you can choose the color for the stopwatch digits and "
"the stopwatch background"
msgstr ""
"Personalisation de color: tu pote seliger le color per cata cifras  e fundo "
"del chronometro"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:27
msgid ""
"Lap times export: you can export the lap times to a file using the JSON or "
"CSV format"
msgstr ""
"Exporta tempore de gyro: tu pote exportar le tempores de gyro in un file per "
"usar formato JSON o CSV"
